---
interface Props {
  buttonText: string;
  affiliateLink: string;
}

const { buttonText, affiliateLink } = Astro.props;
---

<section id="affiliate" class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24">

  <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[32px] bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-800 p-12 text-center text-white shadow-2xl">

    <span class="rounded-full bg-white/20 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-bold">
      Recommended by CreatorStack
    </span>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-5xl font-extrabold">

      Ready to Try VEED?

    </h2>

    <p class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-9 text-blue-100">

      If you're looking for one of the easiest AI video editors available today,
      VEED is an excellent choice for creators, marketers and businesses.

    </p>

    <div class="mt-12">

      <a
        href={affiliateLink}
        target="_blank"
        rel="nofollow sponsored noopener"
        class="inline-flex items-center rounded-2xl bg-white px-10 py-5 text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 transition hover:scale-105"
      >

        🚀 {buttonText}

      </a>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-100">

      <span>✅ Free Plan</span>

      <span>✅ No Credit Card Required</span>

      <span>✅ Cancel Anytime</span>

      <span>✅ Trusted by Millions</span>

    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-blue-200">

      Affiliate Disclosure: We may earn a commission if you purchase through our link,
      at no additional cost to you.

    </p>

  </div>

</section>